2013-01-07|2013-01-13.description: Like many events in Gotham, a simple celebration of the country's birthday exploded into fireworks of a different sort. Now the GCPD get a chance to learn the whole truth...as Batman experienced it! "What Happened Was?" part 3 of 3.
2013-01-07|2013-01-13.name: What Happened Was..., Part 3 of 3

2013-01-28|2013-02-03.description: The quest to find the Eye of the World draws nearer to an end! The group finally makes their way into the cursed northern land known as The Blight - a place fouled by evil in all possible ways - as they continue on their way to the Eye! Also, we discover more about the Warder Lan's mysterious past, and how it ties to the fall of Malkier, a country now consumed by the Blight! All this and a little heartbreak too -- all in the latest issue of Robert Jordan's The Wheel of Time: The Eye of the World!

volume.name: Robert Jordan's Wheel of Time: The Eye of the World

2013-01-28|2013-02-03.description: The dawn before war. Glory and her allies face inevitable death. With only hours left to live, everyone's final moments are revealed in short stories illustrated by some of the greatest new talents in comics, including OWEN GIENI, GREG HINKLE, SLOANE LEONG, JED DOUGHERTY and a very special crossover with EMI LENOX's EMITOWN!
2013-01-28|2013-02-03.name: War Torn, Part Two: Missing In Action

2013-01-28|2013-02-03.description: "Effigy" resumes right where it left off--with Batman none too pleased over the uninvited Batcave appearance of Detective John Jones. But John--aka the Martian Manhunter--is the only one who can help the Dark Knight solve the mystery of the killer roaming under Gotham. The two heroes are going to have to join forces to take down the deadly White Martian.
2013-01-28|2013-02-03.name: Effigy Part Two

2013-03-04|2013-03-10.description: TOXIN'S IN PHILLY. THE DEVIL'S IN JERSEY. VENOM'S GOING TO WAR.
2013-03-04|2013-03-10.name: Toxic Lifestyle

2013-04-01|2013-04-07.description:
Famed movie director Albert Hatchplot is being haunted by the greatest menaces from his most famous movies!

Can Scooby and the gang survive the crazed birds and killer crop dusters long enough to discover the truth?

2013-05-13|2013-05-19.description: The secret origin of the Dark Archer himself is revealed. Check out this can't-miss chapter featuring the Arrow's greatest nemesis--Malcolm Merlyn!
2013-05-13|2013-05-19.name: From the Darkness

2013-06-03|2013-06-09.description: Meet Baseer the All-Seeing, German boy detective, as he joins THE 99 to search for a lost rocket, which mysteriously disappeared from radar moments after a successful launch. But can THE 99 trust someone they just met? Is Baseer all that he seems? And can the lost rocket be found, or will the whole project come crashing down?

2013-06-17|2013-06-23.description: Becky travels a spiritual crossroads that reveals the true power of the Six... what has come before and what might come to pass should the weapons fall into the wrong hands. Skinwalkers, forgotten kingdoms, knights, mythical creatures, and the most fearsome band of outlaws to ever roam the west - they're all set to collide as the strangest of The Sixth Gun adventures continues!
2013-06-17|2013-06-23.name: Ghost Dance, Part Three

2013-06-24|2013-06-30.description:
HELLFIRE SAGA PART 2!

Wolverine has plans for the Bamfs...

Meet the new Hellions!
2013-06-24|2013-06-30.name: The Hellfire Saga Part Two

2013-07-08|2013-07-14.description:
The disturbing conclusion of the 'Quisling' story will prove that even in a world of monsters, you can still be startled by the depravity of civilized man. Christos Gage's tale of ultimate betrayal delivers a brutal psychological punch as Oliver leads Smokey to what he hopes will be a bloody end. But when you toss a match into a powder keg the resulting explosion can be unpredictable. There is no cure. There is no hope. There is only the Crossed.

Available with a Regular cover by Jacen Burrows, Torture cover by Miguel Ruiz, Wraparound cover by Gabriel Andrade, and a special Red Crossed Incentive also by Burrows.

In Black Jack: The Boy Who Came From the Sky, a father will stop at nothing to get his dying son help from the most skilled doctor in the world, Black Jack himself. But when he has to defect from his nation and commit treason to do it, Black Jack doesn't want a foreign nation's armed forces to see him as someone harboring a fugitive! As complications arise, the boy's life is in danger, but can Black Jack help him without getting himself in terrible trouble too? Can Black Jack help him at all? Also included in this issue are Astro Boy: Robot Land, Buddha, and Dororo.

Story Titles

  • Astro Boy: Robot Land Chapter Three
  • Buddha Part Two: The Death of Bandaka Chapter One
  • Dororo: Sebame
  • Black Jack The Boy Who Came From the Sky

2013-08-19|2013-08-25.description: Vampirella finds terror in the heart of Cote de Soleil, an island nation with dark Voudon secrets... and that's not all! A classic Vampi adversary may be hiding in the shadows, and waiting for the perfect moment to strike!

Superman has caught Batman's team inside his fortress. But before he can unleash his fury, he suddenly finds himself in the greatest battle of his life, going head-to-head with Captain Atom. It's an epic battle with deadly consequences!
2013-08-19|2013-08-25.name: Chapter 32

2013-09-16|2013-09-22.description: Meet your new neighbor, Archie! When a vampire vixen moves into a 'haunted' property near Archie's house, strange things start happening. It's weird enough that this mystery woman moved in late at night, but when Archie hears ominous noises coming from her house, he's downright frightened! Is Archie just over-reacting, or is there something sinister going on in Riverdale? Find out in the fearsome first story 'Midnight Madness!'
2013-09-16|2013-09-22.name: MIdnight Madness! Chapter 1

2013-09-23|2013-09-29.description: 'Archie Marries Veronica' - Veronica's trying to stay positive while Archie does the best he can to provide for them in their time of need. Meanwhile, Mr. Lodge is engaged in some secret meetings to keep tabs on business rival Fred Mirth. Kevin Keller is coming to the realization that a job in the Senate is more than he bargained for, especially when the odds are stacked against him. When he uncovers some shocking information about a recent tragedy, does he have what it takes to bring it to light and be the change that everyone needs? 'Archie Marries Betty' - Between Archie's teaching schedule, Ambrose running the New York City Chow House location, and Jughead and Midge's baby on the way, the local Chow House is in desperate need of some help! Meanwhile, Moose is prepping to take a big leap and Cheryl Blossom and Kevin Keller are joining forces in Washington D.C. And speaking of being busy-it looks as though Betty's busy schedule is starting to affect more people than just Archie! Can she mend her relationships before it's too late? Life With Archie has become the hottest spot for amazing variants with some of the best artists around, and this one's no exception! Features a New Yorker-inspired variant cover by Emmy Award Winning writer/artist Dean Haspiel (Billy Dogma, HBO's Bored to Death).
2013-09-23|2013-09-29.name: Love Me, Love My Burger; Baby Showers and Other Bad Weather

"WORLD WAR X" CONTINUES!

UTOPIA's insane plan to end the war

WORLD WAR X claims its first casualties

Will the war finally unite, or divide forever?
2013-10-07|2013-10-13.name: World War X Part Four

2013-10-07|2013-10-13.description: Archie may be the king of high school-but what happens when high school's over? When Reggie introduces him to the Associated College Simulation Program, Archie gets the chance to see what college life will be like - virtually, that is! Archie gets a taste of exams, parties and girls. Will he be able to adjust to college life? Or will this simulated look into his future freak him out even more? Find out in 'College Kidder,' the four-part frenzy that kicks off this fun-filled double digest!
2013-10-07|2013-10-13.name: College Kidder Part One

2013-10-14|2013-10-20.description: The second tale in the Blood Legacy arc. Her world fell apart when her father was brutally murdered by a member of his own family, and now she knows that the only way to survive is to fight back. But this is not the story of Jennifer Blood: this is the story of Vivienne, twelve-year-old daughter of Nicholas Blute, Jen's uncle.
2013-10-14|2013-10-20.name: Blood Legacy 2: Fresh Blood

2013-10-21|2013-10-27.description:
The Man Without Fear--trapped in a nightmare situation!

Something final is building in Daredevil's life--and building fast!

2013-11-25|2013-12-01.description:
Trapped in the future of Barsoom, Dejah Thoris and her descendant battle invading humans in a dark tomorrow. As she struggles to find her way back to her own time, Dejah is confronted with decisions that could change her destiny and alter the history of the red planet!

Tom Judge is no stranger to Hell and the horrors it conjures. In his effort to redeem Jackie Estacado's accursed soul, he finds something much more surprising. But what he won't find represents an even darker omen.

AN OLD RIVALRY REKINDLED

The Grand Magic Games finally begin, but the member of Fairy Tail's team are shocked to find themselves facing off against their old nemesis Raven Tail! They may no longer be a “dark guild,” but as the first round begins Erza's sure there's still something sinister going on. Of course, they'll never know what that might be unless Fairy Tail's team can pull themselves out of last place!

2013-12-09|2013-12-15.description: 'Curse of Ra Moon,' Part Four. The startling, jaw-dropping conclusion to this mega-epic story is here! The tables have turned as the evil Dr. Wily and his sixteen Robot Masters stand shoulder-to-shoulder with Mega Man! But the ominous alien known as Ra Moon still threatens the lives of both the heroes and the villains! Who will survive and what will become of them? One thing is certain-there's no way our hero will be walking away from this one unscathed! Featuring an all-new cover art from Mega-art-guru Patrick 'SPAZ' Spaziante and an awesome new 'payback' variant cover from artist POWREE (Sandra and Woo)!
